<pc>」</pc>從之<pc>，</pc>因詔以<measure quantity="3" unit="households">
<num value="3">三</num>家</measure>
<pc>《</pc>
<title>傳</title>
<pc>》</pc>
<pc>、</pc>
<pc>《</pc>
<title>儀禮</title>
